title: Ex-Div Reminder for Insperity (NSP) - Nasdaq.com
text: Looking at the universe of stocks we cover at Dividend Channel , on 9/6/19, Insperity Inc (Symbol: NSP) will trade ex-dividend, for its quarterly dividend of $0.30, payable on 9/23/19. As a percentage of NSP's recent stock price of $97.35, this dividend works out to approximately 0.31%.
